thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Keybridge Communications to swing to loss in FY 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Keybridge Communications to swing to loss in FY 2017

organizations.name: reuters) - shenzhen keybridge communications co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Shenzhen Keybridge Communications Co Ltd :
* Sees to swing to net loss at 27.5 million yuan to 19.5 million yuan in FY 2017 versus net profit at 2.5 million yuan year ago
* Says more assets impairment loss and higher management expense than expected as main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/oNatwL
